{"tid":1646434,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一定要拎到VTC條CCTV片出黎睇","createTime":"2019-10-11T09:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T11:02:18.000Z","uid":10258,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c508ca47724ddd704fc04d659670d465550ba784","tid":1646434,"uid":10258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在翻查學校CCTV後，見到該名少女於9月19日晚上，將自己的財物放下後，再赤腳往海濱公園方向走去，故認為事件找不到可疑地方。</blockquote><br />\n一定要拎到VTC條CCTV片出黎睇<br />\n<br />\nA: 如果對到CCTV同popo講既唔同，唔洗講，去燒晒18區的警署佢<br />\nB: 如果對到CCTV同popo講既一樣，都未算炒車，要再查清楚係自殺定咩<br />\n<br />\n大家同唔同意？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191011&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60142396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191011%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60142396&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=690ea002\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191011%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60142396&h=3d658227\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191011&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60142396</a>"},{"pid":"f45234c941384fa36dff602af5870448a3fa051b","tid":1646434,"uid":10258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:19:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"730ec41435d29a9505cde03cbd3dae14012cae28","tid":1646434,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:22:49.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"c2756020cb9528ca55e21fa8f7e00680afd3d1ff","tid":1646434,"uid":10258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:33:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81c102f2fd8c1e98cf2689d0b633298c956b3343","tid":1646434,"uid":10258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:33:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17189f97157a1e4faeb05a83948cdcd2dc0dcac3","tid":1646434,"uid":10258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:33:31.000Z","msg